      "rationale": "Test sample characterisation is scoped out because the validation experiments used a single pump unit from the FDA generic pump programme, which is a reference geometry with tight manufacturing tolerances (±0.05 mm). Unit-to-unit variability is not a significant source of uncertainty at MRL 2 for this reference geometry COU."
